name: KyuYong Eom Style LORA
description:
This is my take on KyuYong Eom Style.

I really like his style and hope you guys like this LORA

It was trained over AbyssOrangeMix 2 Hard

All the preview images use

DPM++ 2M 30 Steps 320x320 Hires x2 CFG 8 Denoising at 0.7

Recomended weight: 0.55

modelVersions.description:

It can also be used for Inpainting and works great.
